  "text": "For promoter analysis the indicated genomic sequences were downloaded from Ensembl both for our validated gene set and a randomized set of genes, and analyzed using TESS (http://www. cbil.upenn.edu/tess) [CITATION_1] for TcfLef, XVent1 and Pou5f1 binding sites. Only hits with a log-odd score better than 8.0 were counted. The number of such binding sites for each gene was recorded (Table S1 ) and analyzed with the R program package (http:// www.r-project.org).",
