      "span_text": "For promoter analysis the indicated genomic sequences were downloaded from Ensembl both for our validated gene set and a randomized set of genes, and analyzed using TESS (http://www. cbil.upenn.edu/tess)  for TcfLef, XVent1 and Pou5f1 binding sites."
